3. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is another possible category as the paper deals with a problem that is relevant to AI research. 
4. cs.CL (Computation and Language) is less likely but still possible as the paper involves natural language processing in the form of text descriptions of images. 
5. cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) is also less likely but possible as the paper involves training a neural network to perform comparisons between classes.
